column5: ~~~Lets start with a short 3 hr. video  You guies are so easy, here is my Widdle Gween  Machine, wanna that Steve JoJo who sold it to me, yes Steve she still floaten   A few random shots of my wake up calls    My humble Abode  AAAAAH sunset   Oh Yea I did do some phishen even from shore  Next year you will really suffer my brother Jim will be joining me
